# 🏠 House Price Prediction using Linear Regression

## 📌 Objective
Implement and understand simple & multiple linear regression using Python.

## 🛠 Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Scikit-learn

## 📊 Dataset
House Price Dataset with features like:
- Area
- Bedrooms
- Bathrooms
- Stories
- Parking
- Air Conditioning, etc.

##  Steps Performed
1. Data Preprocessing (handling categorical variables)
2. Train-Test Split
3. Model Training using Linear Regression
4. Model Evaluation (MAE, MSE, R²)
5. Visualization & Coefficient Interpretation

## 📈 Results
- MAE: (970043.4039201641)
